definitions.definition: The place of business of a barber ; a store where a person (usually a male) can go to get a haircut .
A style of a cappella vocal music, sung in four-part harmony, typically by a quartet of men.

main_definition: ( countable ) The place of business of a barber ; a store where a person (usually a male) can go to get a haircut .
